::Torca found himself in the battlefield, ready to fight to the death, but he 
noticed that there was no strategy, and that he would have get orders from 
SOMEONE::
Torca: Torca to base, I need backup. ZZZZZZZZZZ(not responding) Torca to 
Liono, i'm sorry, need your help ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ.  ANYBODY!
::Onyx sees him::
Onyx: I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the end!
::He fires his laser swords at him::
Torca: Aaaaah!!!!!!!!!  Someone come in!
::The last thing he saw was the familier heroic Prime type face with a 
sinister grin::
